{"title":"HTML5初步","date":"2021-03-28T16:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Mar 29, 2021","L":"03/29/2021","MM-DD":"03-29"},"link":"2021/03/29/HTML&CSS/HTML5初步","categories":["HTML&CSS"],"updated":"2021-03-29T03:50:16.480Z","content":"<p>HTML标签不区分大小写，<code>&lt;h1&gt;</code>和<code>&lt;H1&gt;</code>是一样的。</p>\n<h1 id=\"html5\">HTML5<a title=\"#html5\" href=\"#html5\"></a></h1>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><code>&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</code>:文档类型声明，表示该文件为 HTML5文件。<code>&lt;!DOCTYPE&gt;</code> 声明必须是 HTML 文档的第一行，位于 <code>&lt;html&gt;</code> 标签之前</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>&lt;html&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</code>标签对：<code>&lt;html&gt;</code>标签位于HTML文档的最前面，用来标识HTML文档的开始；<code>&lt;/html&gt;</code>标签位于HTML文档的最后面，用来标识HTML 文档的结束；这两个标签对成对存在，中间的部分是文档的头部和主题。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>&lt;head&gt;&lt;/head&gt;</code>标签对：标签包含有关HTML文档的信息，可以包含一些辅助性标签。如<code>&lt;title&gt;&lt;/title&gt;</code>，<code>&lt;link /&gt;&lt;meta /&gt;</code>，<code>&lt;style&gt;&lt;/style&gt;</code>，<code>&lt;script&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</code>等，但是浏览器除了会在标题栏显示<code>&lt;title&gt;</code>元素的内容外，不会向用户显示head元素内的其他任何内容。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>&lt;body&gt;&lt;/body&gt;</code>标签对：它是HTML文档的主体部分，在此标签中可以包含<code>&lt;p&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;br&gt;</code>等众多标签，<code>&lt;body&gt;</code>标签出现在<code>&lt;/head&gt;</code>标签之后，且必须在闭标签<code>&lt;/html&gt;</code>之前闭合。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>注释语法：<code>&lt;!--注释内容--&gt;</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>段落标签：<code>&lt;p&gt;段落文本&lt;/p&gt;</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>自定义文字样式：<code>&lt;span&gt;文本&lt;/span&gt;</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t...</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">style</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">    <span class=\"selector-tag\">span</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">    \t<span class=\"attribute\">color</span>:blue</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">style</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    ...</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span>1922年的春天，一个想要成名名叫尼克•卡拉威（托比•马奎尔Tobey Maguire 饰）的作家，离开了美国中\t\t西部，来到了纽约。那是一个道德感渐失，爵士乐流行，走私为王，股票飞涨的时代。为了追寻他的<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span>美国梦\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span>，他搬入纽约附近一海湾居住。<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>标题<code>&lt;h1&gt;</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>自定义块<code>&lt;div&gt;</code>：在网页制作过程中，可以把一些独立的逻辑部分划分出来，放在一个<code>&lt;div&gt;</code>标签中，这个<code>&lt;div&gt;</code>标签的作用相当于一个容器。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>定义头部区域：<code>&lt;header&gt;</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>定义底部区域：<code>&lt;footer&gt;</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>定义区段：<code>&lt;section&gt;</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>定义侧边栏区域：<code>&lt;aside&gt;</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>水平线标签：<code>&lt;hr&gt;</code></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<p>在html中输入空格、回车是没有作用的：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>换行：<code>&lt;br /&gt;</code>作用相当于word文档中的回车</li>\n<li>空格：要想输入空格，必须写入<code>&amp;nbsp;</code>】</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>无序列表：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span>Item1<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span>Item2<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span>Item3<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>有序列表：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">ol</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span>Item1<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span>Item2<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span>Item3<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">ol</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>为网页添加图片</p>\n<p><code>&lt;img src=&quot;...&quot; alt=&quot;...&quot; title=&quot;...&quot; /&gt;</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>src：标识图像的位置</li>\n<li>alt：指定图像的描述性文本，当图像不可见时（下载不成功时），可看到该属性指定的文本</li>\n<li>title：提供在图像可见时对图像的描述（鼠标滑过图片时现实的文字）</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>为网页添加超链接</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">a</span> <span class=\"attr\">href</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;目标网址&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">title</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;鼠标滑过显示的文本&quot;</span>&gt;</span>链接现实的文本<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">a</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>还可以指定可选的<code>target</code>属性，可选值为<code>_self</code>和<code>_blank</code>，默认值为<code>_self</code>，代表在当前页面打开链接，<code>_blank</code>代表在新窗口打开链接。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>使用<code>table</code>家族为网页添加表格</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">&lt;!-- 表格标签border属性代表给表格加上边框 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">table</span> <span class=\"attr\">border</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;1&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">&lt;!-- 表格标题标签 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">caption</span>&gt;</span>企业员工通讯录<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">caption</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">&lt;!-- tr表示一行 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">&lt;!-- th代表一列，有字体加粗的效果 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    \t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">th</span>&gt;</span>item<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">th</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">th</span>&gt;</span>item<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">th</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">th</span>&gt;</span>item<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">th</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">th</span>&gt;</span>item<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">th</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">&lt;!-- td代表一列，字体为正常效果 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    \t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span>item<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span>item<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span>item<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span>item<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">table</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>使用<code>thead</code>，<code>tbody</code>，<code>tfoot</code>定义表格</p>\n<ul>\n<li>如果不加<code>&lt;thead&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tfoot&gt;</code>，table表格加载完后才显示。加上这些数据结构，<code>tbody</code>包含行的内容下载完优先显示，不必等待表格结束后再显示，同时如果表格很长，用<code>tbody</code>分段，可以一部分一部分地显示。（通俗理解table可以按结构一块块的显示，不再等整个表格加载完后显示）。</li>\n<li><code>&lt;thead&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tfoot&gt;</code>使我们有能力对表格中的行进行分组。这种划分使浏览器有能力支持独立于表格标题和页脚的表格正文滚动，当长的表格被打印时，表格的表头和页脚可被打印在包含表格数据的每张页面上。</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">table</span> <span class=\"attr\">border</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;1&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    \t<span class=\"comment\">&lt;!-- thead标签定义表格的表头 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">thead</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">th</span>&gt;</span>科目<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">th</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">th</span>&gt;</span>分数<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">th</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">thead</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    \t<span class=\"comment\">&lt;!-- tbody标签定义表格的表身 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">tbody</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span>语文<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span>99<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">tbody</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    \t<span class=\"comment\">&lt;!-- tfoot定义表格的表尾 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">tfoot</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span>总分<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span>99<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">tfoot</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">table</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"html5-表单标签，与浏览者互动\">HTML5 表单标签，与浏览者互动<a title=\"#html5-表单标签，与浏览者互动\" href=\"#html5-表单标签，与浏览者互动\"></a></h1>\n<p><strong>网站使用HTML表单（form）与用户交互</strong>。表单是可以把浏览器输入的数据传送到服务器端，这样服务器端程序就可以处理表单传过来的数据。</p>\n<ol>\n<li><code>&lt;form&gt;</code>：成对出现</li>\n<li>action：浏览器输入的数据被传送到的地方，比如一个PHP页面（<code>save.php</code>）</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">form</span> <span class=\"attr\">method</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;传送方法&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">action</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;服务器文件&quot;</span>&gt;</span> </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">form</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>method：数据传送的方式（get/post）</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>所有的表单控件（文本框、文本域、按钮、单选框、复选框等）都必须放在<code>&lt;form&gt;&lt;/form&gt;</code>标签之间（否则用户输入的信息可提交不到服务器上）</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>文本输入框、密码输入框：</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">form</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;text/password&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;名称&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;文本&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">placeholder</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;请输入关键字&quot;</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">form</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>type：<code>type=&quot;text&quot;</code>时，输入框为文本输入框；<code>type=&quot;password&quot;</code>时，输入框为密码输入框。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>name：为文本框命名，已备后台程序ASP、PHP使用。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>value：为文本输入框设置默认值，点击不会消失。（一般起到提示作用）。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>placeholder：输入框占位符，里面可以放提示的输入信息。点击输入框后消失，不是输入框中真正的内容。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>数字输入框：</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;number&quot;</span>/&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><code>input</code>的<code>type</code>属性设置为<code>number</code>，则标识该输入框的类型为数字。数字框只能输入数字，输入其它字符无效。</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>网址输入框：</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;url&quot;</span>/&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><code>input</code>的<code>type</code>属性设置为<code>url</code>，则标识该输入框的类型为网址。数字框的值需以<code>http://</code>或者<code>https://</code>开头,且后面必须有内容,否则表单提交的时候会报错误提示。</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>邮箱输入框：</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;email&quot;</span>/&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><code>input</code>的<code>type</code>属性设置为<code>email</code>，则标识该输入框的类型为邮箱。数字框的值必须包含<code>@</code>，且数字框<code>@</code>之后必须有内容，否则会报错。</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>使用<code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code>标签创建文本域：</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">textarea</span> <span class=\"attr\">rows</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;行数&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">cols</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;列数&quot;</span>&gt;</span>文本<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">textarea</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><code>textarea</code>成对出现</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>在<code>&lt;textarea&gt;&lt;/textarea&gt;</code>之间可以输入默认值</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>cols</code>与<code>rows</code>可以用css样式的<code>width</code>和<code>height</code>来代替。<code>cols</code>用<code>width</code>代替，<code>rows</code>用<code>height</code>代替。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>使用<code>label</code>为<code>input</code>标签穿上衣服：</strong></p>\n<p><code>label</code>标签不会向用户呈现任何特殊效果，它的作用是为鼠标用户改进了可用性。<strong>当用户单击选中该<code>label</code>标签时，浏览器就会自动将焦点转到和标签相关的表单控件上</strong>（就自动选中和该<code>label</code>相关联的表单控件上）。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">label</span> <span class=\"attr\">for</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;控件id名称&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">label</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>注意：标签的<code>for</code>属性中的值应当与相关控件的id属性值相同。e.g.</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;form</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">label</span> <span class=\"attr\">for</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;email&quot;</span>&gt;</span>输入你的邮箱地址<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">label</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;email&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">id</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;email&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">placeholder</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;Enter email&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">form</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>单选框、复选框：</strong></p>\n<p>html中有两种选择框：即单选框和复选框，单选框中的选项用户只能选择一项；复选框中用户可以任意选择多项，甚至全选。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;radio/checkbox&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;值&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;名称&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">checked</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;checked&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol>\n<li>type：当<code>type=&quot;radio&quot;</code>时，控件为单选框；当<code>type=&quot;checkbox&quot;</code>时，控件为复选框；</li>\n<li>value：提交数据到服务器的值（后台PHP使用）；</li>\n<li>name：为控件命名，以备后台程序ASP、PHP使用；</li>\n<li>checked：当设置为<code>checked = &quot;checked&quot;</code>时，该选项默认被选中。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>注意：同一组的单选按钮，name取值一定要一致，e.g.</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">label</span>&gt;</span>性别:<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">label</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">label</span>&gt;</span>男<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">label</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;radio&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;1&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;gender&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">label</span>&gt;</span>女<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">label</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;radio&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;2&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;gender&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>使用select、option标签创建下拉菜单：</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">select</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span> <span class=\"attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;读书&quot;</span>&gt;</span>读书<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span> <span class=\"attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;运动&quot;</span>&gt;</span>运动<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span> <span class=\"attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;音乐&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">selected</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;selected&quot;</span>&gt;</span>音乐<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">select</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><code>select</code>和<code>option</code>都是双标签，它们总是成对出现，需要首标签和尾标签。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>select</code>标签里只能放<code>option</code>标签，标识下拉列表的选项。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>option</code>标签放选项内容，不放置其它标签。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>设置<code>select=&quot;selected&quot;</code>属性，则该选项默认被选中。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>value</code>：<code>value=”提交值&quot;</code>，提交值为向服务器提交的值；<code>&lt;option&gt;</code>中间的值为显示的值。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>提交按钮：</strong></p>\n<p>当用户需要提交表单信息到服务器时，需要用到<strong>提交按钮</strong>。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;submit&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;提交&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol>\n<li>type：只有当<code>type=&quot;submit&quot;</code>时，按钮才有提交作用；</li>\n<li>value：按钮上显示的文字。</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>重置按钮：</strong></p>\n<p>使用重置按钮可以使输入框恢复到初始状态。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;reset&quot;</span> <span class=\"attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;重置&quot;</span>/&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol>\n<li>type：只有当<code>type=&quot;reset&quot;</code>时，按钮才有重置作用；</li>\n<li>value：按钮上显示的文字。</li>\n</ol>\n","prev":{"title":"CSS初步","link":"2021/03/29/HTML&CSS/CSS初步"},"next":{"title":"8.5 对象、类与面向对象编程小结","link":"2021/03/28/JavaScript/8-5-对象、类与面向对象编程小结"},"plink":"http://example.com/2021/03/29/HTML&CSS/HTML5初步/","toc":[{"id":"html5","title":"HTML5","index":"1"},{"id":"html5-表单标签，与浏览者互动","title":"HTML5 表单标签，与浏览者互动","index":"2"}]}